Member Function Documentation

- (AdUnit *) buildAdUnitFromResponseData: (NSData*)  data  

This function builds up an AdUnit containing relevant information about ad to be displayed. the adunit has information about the dimensions,CTA,Click Url and CDATABlock, which is the html-string of the ad.

Parameters:
data The response data fetched from an ad-request made to InMobi server.
Returns:
Returns an autoreleased object of AdUnit.
